Wheaton Precious Metals Corporation

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Silver Wheaton)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search






This article reads like a press release or a news article and/or is entirely based on routine coverage. Please expand this article with properly sourced content to meet Wikipedia's quality standards, event notability guideline, and/or encyclopedic content policy. (March 2015)



Silver Wheaton Corp.





Type

Public


Traded as
TSX: SLW
NYSE: SLW
FWB: SII
S&P/TSX 60 component


Industry
Mining, Silver streaming


Founded
2004


